{"tid":1978762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【記者/議員請入】中聯辦子公司明明唔受法例規管，但都豁免交印花稅","createTime":"2020-04-19T03:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T12:21:38.000Z","uid":40542,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4ede7f5adcb32b513784ed973231d07c1f7b2fc0","tid":1978762,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟睇返立法會文件講中聯辦買樓豁免交印花稅嘅事，有幾個問題。<br />\n<br />\n1. 中聯辦子公司係現有法例底下係<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">不直接適用</span></ins></strong>於現行法例，而係林鄭呢條柒婆用佢嘅<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">特權去豁免</span></ins></strong>徵收中聯辦子公司印花稅！<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>根據《印花稅條例》第41（1）條，<strong><ins>中央人民政府</ins></strong>無須負法律責任繳付任何文書可予徵收的印花稅。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>中央人民政府駐港機構通過其<strong><ins>子公司</ins></strong>在香港購買物業，則第41條並不直接適用，特區政府會<strong><ins>參照第41條的原則</ins></strong>，引用第52（1）條<strong><ins>豁免其相關交易文書的印花稅</ins></strong>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2. 點解講印花稅就可以「按照原則」，將中聯辦子公司同中聯辦地位睇齊，行使香港法例賦予俾「中央人民政府」嘅福利，但講返基本法22條時，就話中聯辦唔係「中央人民政府所屬各部門」，所以不受規管。點解唔可以一樣<strong><ins>「參照第22條的原則」，照樣將中聯辦規管於基本法22條</ins></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n3. 港澳辦明明就係「<strong><ins>國務院辦事機構，國務院系統正部級單位</ins></strong>」，係基本法22條所講嘅「中央人民政府所屬各部門」，點解會扭曲到到唔受規管？<br />\n<br />\n有無記者/議員幫手搞搞佢！！！<br />\n泛民律師黨可唔可以司法覆核！！！"},{"pid":"ab1de81c4edbf6813b3cab54e0eecb8b1f262acc","tid":1978762,"uid":40542,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"另外宜家每日都有幾十位手足上庭，嚟緊仲有幾千單case準備進入法律程序。<br />\n<br />\n被捕組雖然每日整合手足上庭資料，希望大家可以去聲援手足，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">往往好多時公眾席都坐唔爆</span></ins></strong>，去聽審嘅嚟嚟去去都係同一班人，還押手足又得幾丁友送車。<br />\n<br />\n民主派區議員其實有好多人，部份雖然平時都有探還押手足，或聘請被捕手足做野，但可唔可以再<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">做多步，向街坊宣傳吓每日都有班手足上庭</span></ins></strong>，佢地都好想有其他手足聽審<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">聲援佢地</span></ins></strong>，令佢地知道自己唔係孤單寂寞呢？<br />\n<br />\n明白宜家疫情係難搞啲，但疫情過後可否認真考慮吓？"},{"pid":"42b4ad3c2b1cc44b1d1d368f25bbe05a4a8b878c","tid":1978762,"uid":40542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:13:56.000Z","msg":"另外亦請大家養成集慣，<strong><ins>每晚臨訓都去睇被捕人士關注組tg</ins></strong>，睇吓第二日有邊單手足案件可以聽審聲援。<br />\n<br />\n被捕人士關注組tg channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/s/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=150bbe2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nig<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=cf8fa13c\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\n法庭文字直播台（去唔到嘅都唔該睇吓直播，關心吓手足）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=d5500d8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live</a>"},{"pid":"b78f25aedb8c26d544816e82a4188380450beeb0","tid":1978762,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:16:08.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"7e28a026f9068d71221e156a342bdc182f3fad3a","tid":1978762,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7b5b00a090cca24a096cee84ee6aaf4eb03ad91","tid":1978762,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:17:05.000Z","msg":"收稅"},{"pid":"5fd51b4db786ac47702024a02edd687bd1d39fc4","tid":1978762,"uid":234362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:18:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"00a0ecab041f962ccc823b800b4c41f47a429b3b","tid":1978762,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"af6aac66134eeafb6d711f2d706cc0ab373a5c33","tid":1978762,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c